#: ../../files/using_e2ee.rst:3
msgid "Using end-to-end encryption"
msgstr "Ag baint úsáide as criptiú foirceann go foirceann"

#: ../../files/using_e2ee.rst:5
msgid ""
"If enabled server side, Nextcloud provides the possibility to encrypt your "
"files on your devices. This is called end-to-end encryption, or E2EE, "
"because the files are encrypted on your device and only decrypted on your "
"device. The server never sees the unencrypted files, further protecting user"
" privacy and data security."
msgstr ""
"Má tá sé cumasaithe ar thaobh an fhreastalaí, cuireann Nextcloud an "
"fhéidearthacht ar fáil do chuid comhad a chriptiú ar do ghléasanna. Tugtar "
"criptiú ó cheann ceann go ceann, nó E2EE, air seo, toisc go bhfuil na "
"comhaid criptithe ar do ghléas agus nach ndéantar iad a dhíchriptiú ach ar "
"do ghléas. Ní fheiceann an freastalaí na comhaid neamhchriptithe riamh, rud "
"a chosnaíonn príobháideacht an úsáideora agus slándáil sonraí a thuilleadh."

#: ../../files/using_e2ee.rst:10
msgid "Enabling E2EE"
msgstr "Ag cumasú E2EE"

#: ../../files/using_e2ee.rst:12
msgid ""
"If your administrator enabled the [End-to-End Encryption "
"app](https://apps.nextcloud.com/apps/end_to_end_encryption), you can start "
"using it from one of your devices. Open the settings of the Nextcloud client"
" and look for the EE2E encryption settings."
msgstr ""
"Má chuir do riarthóir an aip [Criptiú Deireadh go Deireadh] "
"(https://apps.nextcloud.com/apps/end_to_end_encryption) ar siúl, is féidir "
"leat tosú ag baint úsáide as ó cheann de do ghléasanna. Oscail socruithe "
"chliaint Nextcloud agus féach ar na socruithe criptithe EE2E."

