msgid ""
"It is not possible to enable encryption on a folder in the browser. This "
"must be done on a client app, either a desktop or mobile client."
msgstr ""
"Ní féidir criptiú a chumasú ar fhillteán sa bhrabhsálaí. Ní mór é seo a "
"dhéanamh ar aip chliaint, bíodh sé ina chliant deisce nó soghluaiste."

