#: ../../files/using_e2ee.rst:159
msgid "Adding an E2EE device"
msgstr "Gléas E2EE á chur leis"

#: ../../files/using_e2ee.rst:166
msgid "Setup a new desktop client"
msgstr "Socraigh cliant deisce nua"

#: ../../files/using_e2ee.rst:180
msgid "Setup a new Android device"
msgstr "Socraigh gléas Android nua"

#: ../../files/using_e2ee.rst:194
msgid "Setup a new iOS device"
msgstr "Socraigh gléas iOS nua"

#: ../../files/using_e2ee.rst:208
msgid ""
"In the browser, first enable E2EE in the personal settings. This is needed, "
"as E2EE is less secure in the browser, requiring you to fully trust the "
"administrator to not alter the source code the browser will execute. E2EE "
"folders are currently read-only. Therefore, it is not possible to add, "
"remove, edit, or share an E2EE file from the browser."
msgstr ""
"Sa bhrabhsálaí, cumasaigh E2EE ar dtús sna socruithe pearsanta. Tá gá leis "
"seo, toisc nach bhfuil E2EE chomh slán sa bhrabhsálaí, rud a éilíonn ort "
"muinín iomlán a bheith agat as an riarthóir nach n-athróidh sé an cód foinse"
" a fhorghníomhóidh an brabhsálaí. Tá fillteáin E2EE inléite amháin faoi "
"láthair. Dá bhrí sin, ní féidir comhad E2EE a chur leis, a bhaint, a chur in"
" eagar ná a roinnt ón mbrabhsálaí."

#: ../../files/using_e2ee.rst:211
msgid "Setup a new browser session step 1"
msgstr "Socraigh seisiún brabhsálaí nua céim 1"

