#: ../../files/using_e2ee.rst:234
msgid "Displaying the mnemonic"
msgstr "Ag taispeáint an mnemonic"

#: ../../files/using_e2ee.rst:236
msgid ""
"The mnemonic is a list of words that is used to encrypt and decrypt your "
"files. It is important to keep this mnemonic safe, as it is the only way to "
"access your files if you lose access to your device. If you lose access to "
"your mnemonic, you will lose access to your files."
msgstr ""
"Is liosta focal é an mnemonic a úsáidtear chun do chuid comhad a chriptiú "
"agus a dhíchriptiú. Tá sé tábhachtach an mnemonic seo a choinneáil slán, mar"
" is é an t-aon bhealach é chun rochtain a fháil ar do chuid comhad má "
"chailleann tú rochtain ar do ghléas. Má chailleann tú rochtain ar do "
"mnemonic, caillfidh tú rochtain ar do chuid comhad."

#: ../../files/using_e2ee.rst:243
msgid "Displaying the mnemonic on the desktop client"
msgstr "Ag taispeáint an mnemonic ar an gcliant deisce"

#: ../../files/using_e2ee.rst:257
msgid "Displaying the mnemonic on an Android device"
msgstr "Ag taispeáint an mnemonic ar ghléas Android"

#: ../../files/using_e2ee.rst:271
msgid "Displaying the mnemonic on an iOS device"
msgstr "Ag taispeáint an mnemonic ar ghléas iOS"

#: ../../files/using_e2ee.rst:287
msgid "It is not possible to display the mnemonic in the browser."
msgstr "Ní féidir an mnemonic a thaispeáint sa bhrabhsálaí."
